00:28:37.950 --> 00:28:42.945
The area Stanley believes is safe is now shown in red.

00:28:42.945 --> 00:28:46.405
By matching laser and video data on the fly,

00:28:46.405 --> 00:28:49.250
Stanley can adapt to changing road conditions and

00:28:49.250 --> 00:28:52.310
determine safe driving speeds all by itself.

00:28:52.310 --> 00:28:58.425
Making a car really intelligent requires to give it an ability to adapt.

00:28:58.425 --> 00:28:59.905
It's just like in human life,

00:28:59.905 --> 00:29:04.250
