00:29:04.250 --> 00:29:06.260
We tell them how to learn from contingencies

00:29:06.260 --> 00:29:08.230
and make them smarter and then we trust them to learn.

00:29:08.230 --> 00:29:15.205
Stanford is the only team using adaptive vision to achieve ray speeds.

